<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلُ لَوْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٠٩. <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَوْ»</span>: حَرْفُ شَرْطٍ فِي مُضِيٍّ، وَيَقِلّْ … إِيلَاؤُهَا مُسْتَقْبَلاً، لَكِنْ قُبِلْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٧١٠. وَهْيَ فِي الِاخْتِصَاصِ بِالْفِعْلِ كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِنْ»</span> … لَكِنَّ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَوْ»</span>: <span style="color:#6c6c00">«أَنَّ»</span> بِهَا قَدْ تَقْتَرِنْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧١١. وَإِنْ مُضَارِعٌ تَلَاهَا صُرِفَا … إِلَى الْمُضِيِّ نَحْوُ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَوْ يَفِي كَفَى»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>